sample

public static RegularTimeSeries sample(TimeSeries ts,
                                       TimeInterval ti,
                                       int sampleType)
Creates a regular time series sample every ti (time interval) from the provided time series, ts using last value or interpolation at every point linearly interpolatee value between that point and the next point.

Flags are inherited for last value in the case of LAST_VAL

If the next point does not exist (end of series) then the last value is used.

Parameters:
ts -
ti -
sampleType - either TimeSeriesMath.LINEAR or TimeSeriesMath.LAST_VAL
Returns:
a regular time series with time interval of ti
